43:31.575 --> 43:34.610
Look like you got a yeast
infection on your goddamn face,

43:34.612 --> 43:36.345
you country motherfucker!

43:55.165 --> 43:56.565
Can you make it out of there?

43:56.567 --> 43:59.635
