43:59.637 --> 44:02.304
Goddamn assholes.

44:03.774 --> 44:06.108
Come here, son.

44:06.110 --> 44:07.610
Help me get over this tailgate.

44:07.612 --> 44:09.311
So what time you need us
back in the morning?

44:09.313 --> 44:12.248
