you don't need us back?

44:13.718 --> 44:16.652
We got the job done, didn't we?

44:16.654 --> 44:19.221
This is yours there, son.

44:23.760 --> 44:26.796
We got the job done.
Gary said we got the job.

44:26.798 --> 44:28.397
Joe, I'll do anything you want.

44:28.399 --> 44:32.568
Clear brush anytime, anywhere.
I can do it.

44:32.570 --> 44:34.136
<i>Joe, I'd sure like
