44:34.138 --> 44:37.573
Yeah, maybe later.
I'll let you know.

44:41.311 --> 44:43.646
I don't know what you did

44:43.648 --> 44:45.748
<i>that made that man mad, son.</i>

44:45.750 --> 44:48.184
You hear me?

44:55.392 --> 44:57.126
