45:11.508 --> 45:15.311
Just another day.

45:15.313 --> 45:17.580
It ain't his fault.

45:17.582 --> 45:22.318
He loves us. Just...

45:22.320 --> 45:25.721
He just goes through a hard time.

45:36.433 --> 45:38.167
Well, I ain't gonna
watch him sit there

45:38.169 --> 45:40.636
