that to no one.

45:54.584 --> 45:59.188
<i>You stay with your family.</i>

45:59.190 --> 46:01.724
That's what you need to do.

46:01.726 --> 46:05.327
You need to stay with your family.

46:08.598 --> 46:11.600
Your family's all you got.

46:25.315 --> 46:28.417
What was that?

46:28.419 --> 46:30.719
I don't know.

46:30.721 --> 46:33.956
- Didn't hear no car drive up.
- Probably ain't nobody.

46:33.958 --> 46:36.959
