- Can't taste that.

46:44.935 --> 46:48.204
<i>You want to go out tonight?</i>

46:48.206 --> 46:50.773
Not really.

46:52.776 --> 46:56.345
<i>Where do you want to go?</i>

46:56.347 --> 46:58.380
Hmm...

46:58.382 --> 47:02.651
I don't know.

47:02.653 --> 47:04.687
I was just wondering

47:04.689 --> 47:06.689
