47:34.285 --> 47:37.353
Ah...

47:37.355 --> 47:38.787
There's someone out there.

47:38.789 --> 47:43.359
No. No, wait. Hold this.

47:53.403 --> 47:55.804
Hey, Joe, can you put that dog up?

47:55.806 --> 47:58.907
