48:00.610 --> 48:03.879
Boy, you're soaking-ass wet.

48:03.881 --> 48:06.282
What'd you plan to do,
stand there all night?

48:06.284 --> 48:08.550
He should get out
of them wet clothes.

48:08.552 --> 48:10.286
