- I'm all right.

48:10.288 --> 48:11.854
I just... I just wanted to come by

48:11.856 --> 48:14.356
- and talk to you about working some more.
- Work?

48:14.358 --> 48:15.824
Don't you see what it's
doing out there?

48:15.826 --> 48:18.527
Yes, sir.

48:18.529 --> 48:21.030
Hey, where's my drink at?
You got any trousers he can wear?

48:21.032 --> 48:22.431
What size waist you got?

48:22.433 --> 48:25.634
I think I have some
cool pants he can wear.

48:27.971 --> 48:30.539
I bet nobody come mess 'round
here with that dog out there.

48:30.541 --> 48:31.974
<i>Well, that's why I got the dog.</i>

48:31.976 --> 48:34.543
The dog won't bother anybody
just walking down the road.

48:34.545 --> 48:36.312
Road ain't dogs.

48:36.314 --> 48:37.579
<i>Dog knows what's dogs.</i>

48:37.581 --> 48:38.847
<i>You could have just walked on off,</i>

48:38.849 --> 48:40.049
<i>the dog wouldn't</i>
<i>have done anything.</i>

48:40.051 --> 48:42.451
All right, here. Try these on.

48:42.453 --> 48:44.920
I think they'll fit you.

48:44.922 --> 48:48.057
The bathroom's this way.

48:48.059 --> 48:49.792
<i>The dog is a good dog.</i>

48:49.794 --> 48:53.429
Yeah. That dog scared
the hell out of me, though.

48:54.564 --> 48:56.432
He's all beat up.

48:56.434 --> 48:59.101
Mm-hmm. His daddy.

48:59.103 --> 49:01.570
Saw him do it.

49:02.839 --> 49:04.573
You what?

49:04.575 --> 49:07.476
What, you just sat there

49:07.478 --> 49:09.745
and watched it, or what?

49:09.747 --> 49:12.748
He's a big kid.

49:14.984 --> 49:18.721
