56:35.993 --> 56:37.325
All right. Shake hands.

56:37.327 --> 56:39.361
That's what I'm talking about.
Heck, yeah.

56:39.363 --> 56:41.329
<i>All right, hey, y'all, let's go!</i>

57:09.926 --> 57:13.428
Hey, what you got there?

58:46.656 --> 58:48.390
Hey.

58:48.392 --> 58:50.358
I was wondering if maybe
you could tell me

58:50.360 --> 58:52.227
how to get down to Water Valley.

58:52.229 --> 58:55.630
<i>My wife, she's in</i>
<i>the hospital down there.</i>

58:55.632 --> 58:58.199
<i>I just now got here.</i>

58:58.201 --> 59:01.036
<i>You know how far it is?</i>

59:03.472 --> 59:06.174
Is that the highway
that goes to it?

59:06.176 --> 59:09.311
<i>Is it?</i>

59:09.313 --> 59:10.979
What you drinking?

59:10.981 --> 59:14.983
- Nothing.
- Nothing?

59:18.120 --> 59:21.556
You ain't drinking
some wine, are you?

59:21.558 --> 59:23.391
I may.

59:23.393 --> 59:24.960
Yeah, nothing wrong with that.

59:24.962 --> 59:28.129
Some folks think a feller
ought not drink at all,

59:28.131 --> 59:30.598
but a little drink
never hurt nobody.

59:30.600 --> 59:32.968
That's right.

59:32.970 --> 59:36.471
I get me a little drink every now and
then when I'm down at the house,

59:36.473 --> 59:39.074
but the old lady, she raises
so much sand about it,

59:39.076 --> 59:41.743
I don't do a lot
of drinking down there.

59:41.745 --> 59:45.080
I usually wait till I get
uptown like I am now.

59:45.082 --> 59:47.415
Grab me a drink.

59:49.118 --> 59:51.753
She all right?

59:51.755 --> 59:53.621
Yeah, yeah. She is today.

59:53.623 --> 59:58.026
That's why I'm trying to get down there
to Water Valley, go see about her.

59:58.028 --> 01:00:00.161
I was supposed
to have got paid today,

01:00:00.163 --> 01:00:03.064
but the old fella,
he never showed up,

01:00:03.066 --> 01:00:07.135
you know, so I think I'll
go get me a little drink,

01:00:07.137 --> 01:00:10.438
go down to Water Valley
and go see how she's doing.

01:00:10.440 --> 01:00:12.674
She in the hospital?

01:00:12.676 --> 01:00:16.511
Yeah, she's in the hospital.
She got cancer.

01:00:16.513 --> 01:00:19.347
Just eat up with it all over.

01:00:19.349 --> 01:00:21.616
You know.

01:00:21.618 --> 01:00:24.085
Damn thing, you know,
a person just don't know

01:00:24.087 --> 01:00:25.754
from one day to the next

01:00:25.756 --> 01:00:28.223
which one's gonna be their last.

01:00:33.396 --> 01:00:36.097
Well, it's a beautiful
day out there.

01:00:36.099 --> 01:00:38.700
Feeling a little chill in my bones.

01:00:38.702 --> 01:00:41.636
I think it's fixing to rain.

01:00:41.638 --> 01:00:44.406
<i>It's probably fixing to rain some.</i>

