A little kid.

01:03:08.951 --> 01:03:10.852
Hello, Joe.

01:03:10.854 --> 01:03:13.288
How you doing?

01:03:15.292 --> 01:03:19.494
Oh. Sumbitch.

01:03:20.529 --> 01:03:24.432
